-Aggressive AI<br> Difficult to Get Away from Easy to Stun<br><br>-Weapons<br> Look for Weapons To Slow Down Your Stepsister <br><br>-Puzzles<br> The Puzzles in this Game Is Simple Yet Fun And Wont<br> Be to Hard to Understand",
